    "descriptionModule": {
      "briefSummary": "The purpose of this study is to compare a new noninvasive ventilator to existing ventilators already used for patient care.",
      "detailedDescription": "This study compares the Respironics California V60 Mask ventilator to conventional noninvasive ventilators in a cross-over study with the patient as his/her own control."
    },
